Raspberry Pi for Penetration Testing & Information Security
Compiled and edited by: Stan Urbanek
Dates: Jul 2017 - May 2018

Info: Tools for learning about Information Security 
      Project was setting up a client-server connection between my computer
      and a Raspberry Pi computer to practice penetration testing.

Scripts: 

-> RaspPiLAMP.sh
     = Sets up LAMP server on Raspberry Pi (LAMP = Linux, Apache, MySQL, Python)
-> Server.py and Client.py
     = A generic Server and Client model using sockets and pickle
-> MySQLConnection.py
     = Connect to MySQL server and return MySQLConnection object


